headline: New Study from Realtor.com® Finds Movers Spend More than $17,000 on Average Setting Up Their Homes and Establishing New Routines
summary: With the prime homebuying and moving season around the corner, a new survey from Realtor.com® found that movers spent nearly $17,000 setting up their new homes, compared to nearly $20,000 for movers who used Realtor.com®. This survey also found that while moving often disrupts routines, 36% of movers feel excited on moving day and express excitement throughout the moving process.
